beer.beer_description:
Note: This is a different beer to Redhopulous Maximus. 

American styled red ale. Big chewy malt profile from the judicious use of New Zealand Melanoidin and British Crystal malts – caramel and a hint of chocolate on the back palate. Hopped with Australian Ella and American Chinook hops giving this brew an aroma and character of citrus, tropical fruits and cracked pepper. Perfect with hearty meals and bar snacks.

items.badge_description: The battle for grid iron supremacy is on. Who will be the victor? Who are we kidding, with your favorite brew and this badge, you've already won!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 5 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 2!
